This program has been created with ♥ to everybody who's sick of remember the passwords generate new ones and all over again the same. With this in mind we have created an application that simply puts everything in order, your personal data is encrypted, in meanwhile we have created a list of supported protocols which you may choose between them, once you click on a list item you are getting directly inside of your server.
A special thanks to github.com/hellzerg who helped on the project more than enough!
